title: iRobot Roomba® 700 Series Vacuum Cleaning Robot iAdapt Technology
description:
iAdapt Technology is intuitive and exploratory - it knows where dirt hides and isn't afraid to seek it out. With iAdapt, Roomba chooses from dozens of robotic behaviors more than 60 times per second to ensure complete coverage of every section of your floor.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of iRobot Robotic Vacuums. Shop for the iRobot Roomba 700 Series Robotic Vacuum as well as the full line of iRobot Robotic Vacuums & Floor Care at Abt today!
